      </article>

      <article class="review-card" data-animate="fade-up">
        <div class="review-card__stars" aria-label="5 stars">
          {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <blockquote class="review-card__text">"I've been to several chiropractors, but Dr. Beyerl stands out with his thorough assessments and personalized care plans."</blockquote>
        <p class="review-card__author">Angela H.</p>
        <p class="review-card__tag">General</p>
      </article>

      <article class="review-card" data-animate="fade-up">
        <div class="review-card__stars" aria-label="5 stars">
          {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <blockquote class="review-card__text">"My shoulder mobility has returned to normal after just a few sessions. Dr. Beyerl's expertise in sports injuries is unmatched."</blockquote>
        <p class="review-card__author">Kevin P.</p>
        <p class="review-card__tag">Shoulder</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </SectionWrapper>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <VideoBackground
    videoUrl="https://res.cloudinary.com/dku1gnuat/video/upload/v1773678669/copy_C8C8BA7D-35C3-4286-85F6-927425408BE0_q174of.mp4"
    posterImage="/images/IMG_0954.JPG"
    overlayOpacity={0.7}
    class="cta-premium"
  >
    <div class="container container-narrow" data-animate="fade-up">
      <h2 class="display-3" style="color: var(--color-white); margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);">Ready to feel the difference?</h2>
      <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); max-width: 550px; margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl); line-height: 1.7;">Schedule your first visit and find out what personalized chiropractic care can do for you.</p>
      <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-lg); justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--white btn--lg">Book Your Visit</a>
        <a href="tel:8582777500" class="btn btn--secondary btn--lg" style="background: transparent; border: 2px solid white; color: white;">Call (858) 277-7500</a>
      </div>
    </div>
